{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Fight for survival in an asteroid field</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Rocky Mayhem is a rogue-like survival heavily inspired by the 'Asteroids' game. You play as a pilot, stranded in a mysterious area of space where asteroids try and hit you at every attempt they can, and flying away loops you back to where you once were. The aim of the game is to survive a full 8 minutes while the ship self-repairs all functions before it can escape the asteroid field.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Will you be able to survive the harsh environment of space and escape before your ship is blown to smithereens?</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Play various other modes inspired by other games!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Along with the main game comes Arcade. A small selection of minigames with different objectives. Fight against sentient asteroids, the intergalactic police, or take a chill search in a maze of tunnels for a stranded drillship. With constant updates to these minigames, there's nothing that you won't enjoy.\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Current modes include:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Rescue Operations </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Most Wanted</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Red Light, Green Light </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Search and Destroy</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1303350/extras/image_2024-09-19_224222973.png?t=1730932235\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Customize your ship with unlockable cosmetics</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Play and unlock unique styles for your ship. With an increasing library of skins, there'll be a skin that suits everyone.\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1303350/extras/image_2